# Usage instructions for main.py with config file
source venv311/bin/activate

## Command
python main.py <text|text_file> <output_file> [config_file]

- <text|text_file>: Text to synthesize or a file containing text
- <output_file>: Path to save synthesized audio
- [config_file]: Optional YAML config file (default: config.yaml)

## Config file options (YAML)
- randomness: Controls voice randomness(Tempurature) (float, e.g., 0.5)
- sample_cache: Name of cache file for voice samples (string)
- reference_folder: Folder containing reference .wav files (string)

Example config.yaml:

randomness: 0.5
sample_cache: "voice_samples_cache.pt"
reference_folder: "voices/Default"

## Example command
python main.py "Hello World!" output.wav Default.yaml

